@startuml
!theme plain
title 19. Pod Network and RoCEv2 Tuning
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Traffic classes" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "RoCEv2 fabric" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "PFC/ECN/DCQCN" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Rail/DPU mapping" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Admission telemetry" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : DSCP/PCP
N2 --> N3 : RDMA packets
N3 --> N4 : congestion control
N4 --> N5 : affinity

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
